{"tid":2192210,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中國8月美元計出口按年增長9.5%勝預期 進口跌2.1%遜預期","createTime":"2020-09-07T03:35:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T03:39:21.000Z","uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"df5f531b02f8648822e6b5dcb6149a8091d5add8","tid":2192210,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:35:19.000Z","msg":"中國海關總署周一（7日）公布，以美元計，中國8月出口按年增長9.5%，好過市場預期的7.5%，7月為增長7.2%；進口跌2.1%，跌幅較7月擴大0.7個百份點，預期為增長0.2%。<br />\n<br />\n分析指出，隨著各國新冠肺炎防疫措施陸續解封，恢復經濟活動，帶動外需延續增長。<br />\n<br />\n據海關總署，以人民幣計，中國8月出口按年增長11.6%；進口轉跌0.5%，7月為增長1.6%。貿易順差4165.9億元，增加74.4%。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2745830/中國8月美元計出口按年增長9.5-勝預期%C2%A0進口跌2.1-遜預期\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2745830%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B8%E6%9C%88%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E8%A8%88%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%8C%89%E5%B9%B4%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%B79.5-%E5%8B%9D%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F%25C2%25A0%E9%80%B2%E5%8F%A3%E8%B7%8C2.1-%E9%81%9C%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp8WiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=b53e25a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2745830/中國8月美元計出口按年增長9.5-勝預期%C2%A0進口跌2.1-遜預期</a>（更新版）<br />\n<br />\n中國又蠃 All in A股<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd079682a79d7f6ef2ee8718c8ada8be2df060b","tid":2192210,"uid":290883,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:37:20.000Z","msg":"冇水災，冇飢荒，大豐收！"},{"pid":"65a955f36f7d3dfff1f9ed318c3ca70b39b98451","tid":2192210,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dbd079682a79d7f6ef2ee8718c8ada8be2df060b","tid":2192210,"uid":290883,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:37:20.000Z","msg":"冇水災，冇飢荒，大豐收！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:39:21.000Z","msg":"根本咩事都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/